{
  "stem": "1858.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 287.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the end of 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- first, even before that, they terrorized us in different ways, such as I remember one day-- do you mind if I go back?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day they came and asked my father for his identification card.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went to each household and they asked for the IDs of each man of the home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that they were going to hang three people and they wanted people from each home to witness it so as to instill fear in all of us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'll never forget that because that day we kids were playing in the street, and we found out that they are going to hang three men.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we thought, oh, let's go and see, as though this was some kind of a circus, or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have never seen a Western movie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have never witnessed a hanging, so it was a novelty.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was something like exciting, something new.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we all ran into the square also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll never forget it as I was standing there and waiting, not knowing what I was about to see.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a gorgeous, sunny day, and unconsciously, or subconsciously, I was humming to myself a song that Jeanette MacDonlad sang in the movie about San Francisco, San Francisco, this has Polish words to it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was humming that song to myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, a horrible scream went out from the whole crowd, and I looked up and saw the three men hanging.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot forget the sight because of the song.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whenever I hear that melody-- on the radio, on television, or wherever-- I see the three men hanging.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So those are things that I can't forget because of a song.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Others can probably forget because they viewed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
